name: CYBERWALL_BREACH
description:
Oh no! Your computer is infected with viruses!!!! They're wrecking havoc on all your files!!! But what's this?? Your antivirus; it's woken up from it's sleep!!!! It's come here to save the day!!!

CYBERWALL_BREACH is a short 3D Platformer about an antivirus who needs to get the computer rid of all the nasty viruses that have entered the computer. You need to run, jump and attack enemies on a small level filled with little details and secrets (🤔😏😏). How fast can you go? How high can you score?

Disclaimer: This game does not contain actual viruses - only cakes and spaghetti code 🍝🍝🍝
